<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1776,2032]" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
1 Scutum not densely bristled, with only few acrostichal (acr) and dorsocentral (dc) bristles (
<figureCitation box="[1088,1234,1776,1797]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Figs 24, 26, 30</figureCitation>
). Fore and mid tibiae yellow (
<figureCitation box="[303,448,1805,1826]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Figs 23, 25, 29</figureCitation>
)............................................................................... 2
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1776,2032]" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
- Scutum densely bristled, bearing several rows of acr and dc bristles (
<figureCitation box="[879,989,1835,1856]" captionStart="FIGURES 16–19" captionStartId="13.[151,264,1730,1752]" captionTargetBox="[168,1402,209,1682]" captionTargetId="figure@13.[168,1402,209,1682]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURES 16–19. Crossopalpus pennescens (Melander, 1918) (Holotype ♀, NMNH). 16. Lateral habitus; 17. Frontal habitus; 18. Dorsal habitus; 19. Labels. Scale bars = 0.5mm. Figures kindly provided by Alyssa Seemann, National Museum of Natural History (NMNH), Smithsonian Institution." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626756/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Figs 16, 18</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[999,1026,1835,1856]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">28</figureCitation>
). At least fore or mid tibiae darkened (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURES 10–11" captionStartId="9.[151,264,683,705]" captionTargetBox="[154,1387,199,662]" captionTargetId="figure@9.[151,1436,193,662]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 10–11. Crossopalpus armipes (Bezzi, 1909) (Holotype ♀, SMTD). 10. Lateral habitus; 11. Labels. Scale bar = 0.5 mm. Figures kindly provided by Uwe Kallweit, from Senckenberg Museum für Tierkunde Dresden (SMTD)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626752/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Figs 10</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[261,323,1864,1885]" captionStart="FIGURES 16–19" captionStartId="13.[151,264,1730,1752]" captionTargetBox="[168,1402,209,1682]" captionTargetId="figure@13.[168,1402,209,1682]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURES 16–19. Crossopalpus pennescens (Melander, 1918) (Holotype ♀, NMNH). 16. Lateral habitus; 17. Frontal habitus; 18. Dorsal habitus; 19. Labels. Scale bars = 0.5mm. Figures kindly provided by Alyssa Seemann, National Museum of Natural History (NMNH), Smithsonian Institution." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626756/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">16, 17</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[333,359,1864,1885]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">27</figureCitation>
), reddish-yellow to brown................................................................... 4
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1776,2032]" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
2 Frons and vertex with patch of white tomentum (
<figureCitation box="[701,774,1893,1914]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Fig. 24</figureCitation>
). Antennae black, postpedicel concolorous with preceding segments (
<figureCitation box="[231,343,1923,1944]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Figs 23, 24</figureCitation>
). Femora concolorous, yellow (
<figureCitation box="[646,759,1923,1944]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Figs 23–24</figureCitation>
). Shorter species, about 
<quantity box="[991,1046,1923,1944]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="112" unit="mm" value="1.0">1 mm</quantity>
............... 
<taxonomicName authority="Freitas-Silva &amp; Ale-Rocha, 2019" authorityName="Freitas-Silva &amp; Ale-Rocha" authorityYear="2019" box="[1226,1353,1923,1944]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Crossopalpus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="112" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="albivertex" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1226,1353,1923,1944]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">C. albivertex</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1359,1436,1922,1944]" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1359,1436,1922,1944]" pageId="1" pageNumber="112" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1776,2032]" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
<keyLead pageId="1" pageNumber="112">
- Frons and vertex without patch of white tomentum (
<figureCitation box="[729,842,1952,1973]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Figs 26, 30</figureCitation>
). Antennae dark brown to yellow, postpedicel lighter in color than preceding segments (
<figureCitation box="[474,622,1981,2002]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Figs 26, 29, 30</figureCitation>
). Hind femur darker than fore and mid femora (
<figureCitation box="[1079,1191,1981,2002]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="112">Figs 25, 29</figureCitation>
). Longer species, about 
<quantity metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="112" unit="mm" value="2.0">2 mm</quantity>
............................................................................................... 3
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="2" pageNumber="113">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,151,559]" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">
<keyLead pageId="2" pageNumber="113">
3 Palpus (
<figureCitation box="[303,375,151,172]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">Fig. 29</figureCitation>
) and abdomen yellow (
<figureCitation box="[606,721,151,172]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">Figs 29, 30</figureCitation>
). Hind tibia darkened (
<figureCitation box="[948,1021,151,172]" captionStart="FIGURES 23–30" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1802,1824]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[151,1436,193,1781]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 23–30. Crossopalpus Bigot. Male habitus. 23–24. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 23. Lateral view; 24. Dorsal view; 25–26. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA). 25. Lateral view; 26. Dorsal view; 27–28. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, CZMA); 27. Lateral view; 28. Dorsal view; 29–30. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Holotype ♂, INPA); 29. Lateral view; 30. Dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626760/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">Fig. 29</figureCitation>
). Wing milky, with no infuscation, second costal section 2/3 length of third costal section (
<figureCitation box="[683,753,181,202]" captionStart="FIGURES 31–35" captionStartId="17.[151,264,1149,1171]" captionTargetBox="[151,1433,198,1104]" captionTargetId="figure@17.[151,1436,193,1128]" captionTargetPageId="17" captionText="FIGURES 31–35. Crossopalpus Bigot. Wings. 31. Crossopalpus albivertex sp. nov. (Paratype ♂, Cabaceiras, Paraíba, INPA); 32. Crossopalpus aliceae sp. nov. (Paratype ♂, Umuarama, Paraná, INPA); 33. Crossopalpus armipes (Bezzi, 1909) (Holotype ♀, Tacna, SMTD); 34. Crossopalpus goliathus sp. nov. (Paratype ♂, Ubajara, Ceará, INPA); 35. Crossopalpus xanthogaster sp. nov. (Paratype ♀, Zongo, La Paz, INPA). Scale bars = 0.5 mm. Figure 33 kindly provided by Uwe Kallweit, from Senckenberg Museum für Tierkunde Dresden (SMTD)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2626763/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="113">Fig. 35</figureCitation>
).................................... 
